<TEXT>
silent movie star aileen pringle who had 
leading roles in in more than 60 movies has died she was 94 
she died saturday in her manhattan home 
her movies in which she often played an exotic siren included 
three weeks souls for sale puttin on the ritz 
adam and eve and a kiss in the dark 
her leading men included john gilbert in adventure movies and 
lew cody in domestic farces 
a native of san francisco she was born aileen bisbee 
she was married to charles mck pringle the son of a former 
governor of jamaica and to novelist james m cain both marriages 
ended in divorce 
