the sensation that the house panel did with its parade of witnesses 
invoking 5th amendment rights 
dalemberte is a former dean of the florida state university law 
school and presidentelect of the american bar association 
graham said his panel would focus instead on vulnerability 
to abuse in housing laws and probably would not try to compel 
testimony from witnesses who have refused before the lantos panel 
he said it would conclude hearings in 60 to 90 days 
